This is attempt to generate training images for text detection and recognition
## generate_text_in_image.cpp 
This scrip is complete with opencv, and will generate letters on the random background image, with the size and color of letter is also random
## generate_xml_annotation.py
Read the couts of generate_text_in_image and generate xml for each image, as the type of VOC.
Call python generate_xml_annotation.py:
    (1) first, generate dirs
    (2) generate_text_in_image in /dirs/JPEGImages
    (3) generate_xml_annotation in /dirs/Annotations

After generate, use paras_xmls.py to analysis xmls, both print one xml, or do statistics
